This paper involves the use of deep reinforcement learning, deep neural networks, and control theory to develop a guidance law for intercepting a maneuvering target. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
